Dīn (Arabic: دين, romanized: Dīn, also anglicized as Deen) is an Arabic word

Verse 2:256
لَآ إِكْرَاهَ فِى ٱلدِّينِ ۖ

Let there be no compulsion in Deen

So, what is deen?
> Deen is comprised of five systems
   1) itikadi system - Religion or mazhab
   2) Aqlaqi system - Morality & Manners
   3) muaashartii system - Social system, community lifestyle in social places. For example: Alcohol in Birthday Vs Meat party
   4) Muashi system - Financial system
   5) Amli system - How to implement all four(above)?

